	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=280096><span id= >bdfoster</span></a><br><span id=notbold>44 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.50]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Your modifier percentages are wrong.<br><br>String mod of 3.4 is not 34% but 340% of base.<br>A modifier of 1 is base, 100%.<br>A modifier of 2 is double base, 200%<br>So a song that has a base of say (for numbers only) 100Damage per tick is going to do the following...<br><br>Mod 1.0 = 100<br>Mod 1.5 = 150<br>Mod 2.0 = 200<br>Mod 2.6 = 260<br>Mod 3.4 = 340<br><br>Bard epic is mod of 80 this means it can boost a song that does 100 damage to 180.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Shassiash Bard of 65 Compositions<br><a href="http://www.eqdiva.com" target=_new>http://www.eqdiva.com</a> EQDiva playground and school of the bards</td></tr>
